|                     | bar    | bar                      | 1 bar = 100 kPa                |
+---------------------+--------+--------------------------+--------------------------------+
|                     | atm    | atmosphere               | 1 atm = 101.325 kPa            |
+---------------------+--------+--------------------------+--------------------------------+
| viscosity           | poise  | poise                    | 1 poise = 0.1 Pa s             |
+---------------------+--------+--------------------------+--------------------------------+
| energy/work         | J      | joule                    | 1 J = 1 N m                    |
+---------------------+--------+--------------------------+--------------------------------+
|                     | cal    | calorie                  | 1 cal =  4.1868 J              |
