| power               | W      | watt                     | 1 W = 1 J s⁻¹                  |
+---------------------+--------+--------------------------+--------------------------------+
| temperature         | K      | kelvin                   | SI base unit                   |
+---------------------+--------+--------------------------+--------------------------------+
